---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About"
	description="Internet Archaeologist. Michelada Connoisseur. Digital art & crypto researcher since 2012. Founder of 0773H."
>
	<header class="about-header">
		<p class="about-eyebrow">/about</p>
		<h1 class="about-title">Gramajo</h1>
		<p class="about-tagline">
			Internet Archaeologist. Michelada Connoisseur. Digital art &amp; crypto researcher since 2012.
			Founder of 0773H – a media and research company producing podcasts, video content, and weekly analysis reports.
		</p>
	</header>

	<section class="about-section">
		<h2>Work &amp; research</h2>
		<p>
			I investigate how decentralized networks preserve (or erase) their own history. That means digging through forgotten
			governance proposals, resurfacing early NFT experiments, and mapping the archeology of token communities. The research
			fuels long-form audio, video essays, and high-signal briefs for founders, curators, and onchain investigators.
		</p>
		<p>
			From 2012 onward, I've been cataloging crypto's cultural artifacts—collecting oral histories, interviewing protocol
			designers, and documenting how communities evolve when code and capital collide. The archive keeps growing, and every
			project is another layer in the sediment.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="about-section">
		<h2>Contact</h2>
		<dl class="about-contact">
			<div>
				<dt>Email</dt>
				<dd><a href="mailto:onchainaliens@gmail.com">onchainaliens@gmail.com</a></dd>
			</div>
			<div>
				<dt>Signal</dt>
				<dd><span>gramajo.04</span></dd>
			</div>
			<div>
				<dt>Telegram</dt>
				<dd><a href="https://t.me/jgramajo4">jgramajo4</a></dd>
			</div>
		</dl>
	</section>

	<section class="about-section">
		<h2>Support the work</h2>
		<p>
			If the research is useful, consider backing the archive so more interviews, reconstructions, and network autopsies
			can ship faster.
		</p>
		<a class="about-cta" href="/donation">Support the archive ↗</a>
	</section>

	<section class="about-section">
		<h2>Decentralized mirror</h2>
		<p>
			A decentralized copy of this site lives on <a href="https://gramajo.eth.limo" rel="noopener noreferrer">gramajo.eth.limo</a>.
			It updates alongside the canonical version and stays resilient even if this server goes dark.
		</p>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about-header {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}
	.about-eyebrow {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}
	.about-title {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 3.2rem);
	}
	.about-tagline {
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 60ch;
		color: var(--color-muted);
		font-size: 0.98rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}
	.about-section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.9rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}
	.about-section:last-of-type {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
	.about-section h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}
	.about-section p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}
	.about-contact {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.85rem;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}
	.about-contact div {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.2rem;
	}
	.about-contact dt {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-muted);
	}
	.about-contact dd {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
	.about-contact a {
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}
	.about-cta {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.35rem;
		padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
		border-radius: calc(var(--radius-card) / 1.5);
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		transition: background var(--transition-base), color var(--transition-base);
	}
	.about-cta:hover,
	.about-cta:focus-visible {
		background: var(--color-accent);
		color: var(--color-bg);
	}
	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.about-header {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}
		.about-tagline {
			font-size: 0.92rem;
		}
	}
</style>
